[
    {
        "source_sentence": "釋家觀化還愚經",
        "translation": "Sutra on the Śākyas' Contemplation of the Transformation of Society and the Return of Folly",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c03_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "昔舍衛國有一貧家。",
        "translation": "Once there was a poor family in Śrāvastī.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c05_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夫婦慳惡不信道德。",
        "translation": "The couple was stingy and disbelieved in morality.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c05_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛愍其愚現為沙門。",
        "translation": "The Buddha pitied their foolishness and made them into an ascetic.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c05_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "詣門分衛。",
        "translation": "He went to their home and guarded them.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c06_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時夫不在。",
        "translation": "The husband wasn't there at the time.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c06_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其婦罵詈無有道理。",
        "translation": "The woman ridiculed him without reason.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c06_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "沙門語曰。",
        "translation": "The ascetic said.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c07_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "吾為道士。",
        "translation": "\"I'm a practitioner of the Way.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c07_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乞匃自活。",
        "translation": "I'm begging for my own life.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c07_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不惡罵詈。",
        "translation": "I don't hate to scold.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c08_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "唯望一食耳。",
        "translation": "I just want a meal.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c08_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "主人婦曰。",
        "translation": "The host woman said.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c08_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若汝立死食尚叵得。",
        "translation": "'If you were to propose death as a meal, you wouldn't be able to get it.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c08_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "況今平健欲望我食。",
        "translation": "How much more so now that you're healthy and want food for me?",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c09_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "但稽留時節不如早去。",
        "translation": "But it's better to wait for the right time than to leave early.'",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c09_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於是沙門住立其前。",
        "translation": "The ascetic then stood in front of her.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c10_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "載眼杼氣便現立死。",
        "translation": "He put on his eyes and loomed his breath, and then he appeared to be standing dead.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c10_16",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "身體膖脹鼻口蟲出。",
        "translation": "His body is bloated, and worms are coming out of his nose and mouth.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c11_17",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "腹潰腸爛不淨流漫。",
        "translation": "His belly is full of flesh, his intestines are rotten, and he's impure and disgusting.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c11_18",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其婦見此恐怖失聲棄而捨走。",
        "translation": "When the woman saw this, she was terrified, lost her voice, and abandoned herself.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c12_19",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於是道人忽然捨去。",
        "translation": "The practitioner then suddenly left.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c13_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "去捨數里坐樹下息。",
        "translation": "He went away for a few miles, sat down under a tree, and took a rest.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c13_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其夫來歸道中見婦。",
        "translation": "Her husband came back to the road and saw the woman there.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c13_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "怪其驚怖。",
        "translation": "He was surprised and frightened.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c14_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其婦語夫。",
        "translation": "The woman said to her husband.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c14_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有一沙門見怖如此。",
        "translation": "\"There was an ascetic who saw how frightened she was.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c14_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夫大瞋恚問為所在。",
        "translation": "The husband was furious and asked where she was.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c15_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "婦曰已去。",
        "translation": "The woman said she had left.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c15_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "想亦未遠。",
        "translation": "She thought she hadn't gone far.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c16_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夫即執弓帶刀尋迹往逐。",
        "translation": "The husband then took his bow and knife and followed her trail.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c16_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "張弓拔刀奔走。",
        "translation": "He opened his bow, drew his sword, and ran away.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c16_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "直前欲斫道人。",
        "translation": "He ran straight ahead intending to attack the Daoist.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c17_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "道人即化作瑠璃城。",
        "translation": "The Daoist then transformed himself into a beryl city.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c17_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以自圍繞。",
        "translation": "He surrounded himself with it.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c18_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其人遶城數匝不能得入。",
        "translation": "The man circled the city several times and couldn't get inside.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c18_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "問道人何不開門。",
        "translation": "He asked the Daoist why he didn't open the gate.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c18_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "道人曰。",
        "translation": "The Daoist said.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c19_16",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "欲所門開棄汝弓刀。",
        "translation": "\"Do you want the gate to be opened and your bow and sword to be discarded?",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c19_17",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其人自念當隨其語。",
        "translation": "The man thought to himself, 'I will follow his words.'",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c20_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若當得入手拳加之。",
        "translation": "If he could get in, he would hit him with his fist.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c20_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "尋棄弓刀。",
        "translation": "He then looked for him and threw away his bow and sword.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c20_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "門故不開。",
        "translation": "That's why the door wasn't opened.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c21_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "語道人曰。",
        "translation": "He said to the religious practitioner.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c21_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "已棄弓刀。",
        "translation": "\"I've thrown away my bow and sword.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c21_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "門何不開。",
        "translation": "Why didn't he open the door?",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c21_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "道人曰。",
        "translation": "The Daoist said.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c22_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "吾使汝棄心中惡意弓刀耳。",
        "translation": "\"I'm asking you to throw away the malicious bow and knife in your heart.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c22_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "非謂手中弓刀也。",
        "translation": "I don't mean the bowie knife in your hand.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c22_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於是其人心驚體悸。",
        "translation": "That man's heart was startled and his body was convulsed.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c23_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "道人神聖乃知我心。",
        "translation": "The Daoist's sagacity then knew my thoughts.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c23_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即便叩頭悔過。",
        "translation": "He quickly bowed his head and repented.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c24_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "啟道人曰。",
        "translation": "He asked the man of the Way.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c24_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我有弊妻不識真人。",
        "translation": "'I have a bad wife who doesn't know the real person.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c24_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "使我與怨。",
        "translation": "She made me get into trouble with him.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c25_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願小垂慈莫便捨。",
        "translation": "Please don't let her go because of some small mercy.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c25_16",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今欲將來勸令修道。",
        "translation": "Now, I want to encourage you to cultivate your faith in the future.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c26_17",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即起還歸。",
        "translation": "He then got up and returned.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c26_18",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其妻問曰。",
        "translation": "His wife asked him.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c26_19",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "沙門所在。",
        "translation": "\"Where's the ascetic?",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c27_20",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其夫具說神之德。",
        "translation": "Her husband spoke of the ascetic's virtues.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c27_21",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今者在彼鄉。",
        "translation": "'He's now in his hometown.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c27_22",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "宜自往改悔滅罪。",
        "translation": "He should go by himself to repent and end his sins.'",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c28_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於是夫妻至道人所。",
        "translation": "The couple then went to the Wayfarer.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c28_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五體悔過願為弟子。",
        "translation": "They repented of their sins in five parts and vowed to become his disciples.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c28_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "長跪問曰。",
        "translation": "They knelt down and asked him.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c29_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "道人神變聖達乃爾。",
        "translation": "\"Is this the Daoyin's miraculous and noble accomplishment?",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1462c29_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有瑠璃城堅固難踰。",
        "translation": "'There's a beryl city that's sturdy and hard to surpass.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1463a01_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "志明意定永無憂患。",
        "translation": "His mind is clear, his thoughts are focused, and he's never in trouble.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1463a01_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "行何道德致此神妙也。",
        "translation": "What ethics does he practice that makes him so marvelous?",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1463a02_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "道人答曰。",
        "translation": "The Daoist replied.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1463a02_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "吾博學無厭奉法。",
        "translation": "\"I'm a man of extensive learning who never tires of following the Dharma.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1463a02_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不懈精進持戒慧不放逸。",
        "translation": "I don't neglect diligence, maintain precepts, and don't let myself get carried away with wisdom.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1463a03_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "緣是得道。",
        "translation": "Because of this, I've attained the way.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1463a03_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自到泥洹。",
        "translation": "I'll reach nirvāṇa naturally.'",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1463a04_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於是道人因說偈言。",
        "translation": "The native then spoke a verse, saying.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1463a04_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　多聞持堅固　　奉法為垣墻　　精進難踰毀　從是戒慧成　　多聞令志明　　已明智慧增　智則博解義　　見義行法安　　多聞能除憂　能以定為歡　　善說甘露法　　自知得泥洹　聞為知法律　　解疑亦見□　　從聞捨非法　行至不死處道人說偈已現佛光相。",
        "translation": "\"Being well-versed and resolute, upholding the Dharma as a wall, and making effort that's hard to surpass, thus accomplishing morality and wisdom, hearing much makes one's intentions clear, and insight and wisdom increase. Wisdom then fully understands the meaning, sees the meaning, and practices the Dharma with peace. Being well-versed removes grief, makes concentration a joy, and skillfully explains the nectar-like Dharma. He knows he's attained nirvāṇa, understands the Dharma, resolves doubts, and sees the □ From hearing, he abandons what's not the Dharma, travels to the place of immortality, and then the practitioner's verse reveals the Buddha's radiant features.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1463a05_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "洪暉赫奕照耀天地。",
        "translation": "His radiance shines brilliantly, illuminating heaven and earth.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1463a11_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夫婦驚愕精神戰懼。",
        "translation": "The couple was startled and their spirits fought in fear.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1463a12_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "改怨洗心頭腦打地。",
        "translation": "They changed their enmity, washed their minds, and beat their heads to the ground.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1463a12_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "壞二十億惡得須陀洹道。",
        "translation": "They destroyed two billion evils and attained the stream-winner path.",
        "source": "T85n2918_001:1463a12_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    }
]